text: Svitlana Fil (born 4 May 1969) is a Soviet rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Unified Team Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
